- You're safe here!

210
00:10:30.193 --> 00:10:32.819
What is... What's happening?

211
00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:33.987
I know. I know!

212
00:10:33.988 --> 00:10:35.655
I told you not to
pull down the tree!

213
00:10:35.656 --> 00:10:37.032
