238
00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:39.803
[creatures screeching]

239
00:11:39.804 --> 00:11:41.012
- Dad!
- We gotta go!

240
00:11:41.013 --> 00:11:44.182
- Boyd!
- [creatures screeching]

241
00:11:44.183 --> 00:11:45.059
[creatures screeching]

242
00:11:49.105 --> 00:11:50.480
