the fuck up back there!

292
00:13:47.640 --> 00:13:49.766
[Boyd] Okay.
Hey. look. everybody. easy.

293
00:13:49.767 --> 00:13:51.184
You're okay. Take it easy.

294
00:13:51.185 --> 00:13:53.853
Listen. take...
take deep breaths. all right?

295
00:13:53.854 --> 00:13:55.355
Take deep breaths.

296
00:13:55.356 --> 00:13:56.773
You're gonna...
we're almost back to town.

297
00:13:56.774 --> 00:13:58.275
We are...

298
