317
00:14:35.313 --> 00:14:36.896
- Are you fucking...
- [sobbing]

318
00:14:36.897 --> 00:14:38.315
It's okay.

319
00:14:38.316 --> 00:14:41.234
Oh. shit. shit!
Ahh! Keep going!

320
00:14:41.235 --> 00:14:43.862
- [Acosta] Okay! I'm going!
- [sobbing]

321
00:14:43.863 --> 00:14:45.905
